Courses

Explore our courses and choose the one that best fits your needs.

AI and Data Science Fundamentals

Duration: 24 weeks

Provides foundational knowledge and practical skills in AI and Data Science, preparing students for entry-level positions.

  • Introduction to AI and Data Science
  • Python Programming for AI
  • Statistics and Probability for Data Science
  • Data Wrangling and Visualization
  • Version Control (Git)
  • Python Development
  • Backend Development
  • Frontend Development
  • Machine Learning Basics
  • Introduction to Deep Learning
  • Project Work and Case Studies

Outcome: Solid foundation in AI and Data Science, enabling further specialization or entry-level roles in data analytics, machine learning, and AI development.

AI Engineering Advanced

Duration: 12 weeks

Provides in-depth knowledge and hands-on experience in AI engineering, focusing on the design and implementation of AI systems.

  • Advanced Machine Learning Techniques
  • Deep Learning and Neural Networks
  • Natural Language Processing (NLP)
  • Computer Vision
  • AI Model Optimization and Deployment
  • AI Ethics and Governance
  • Capstone Project

Outcome: Ability to design, develop, and deploy advanced AI systems, preparing them for roles such as AI Engineer, Machine Learning Engineer, and AI Specialist.

ML Deployment Advanced

Duration: 12 weeks

Focuses on the practical aspects of deploying machine learning models in real-world scenarios, emphasizing scalability, efficiency, and integration.

  • Model Deployment Strategies
  • Cloud Platforms for AI (AWS, Azure, Google Cloud)
  • MLOps (Machine Learning Operations)
  • Model Monitoring and Maintenance
  • Case Studies on Successful Deployments
  • Final Deployment Project

Outcome: Expertise in deploying and managing machine learning models, making them suitable for roles in AI operations, MLOps engineering, and data engineering.
